-Richard-M Richard Nixon Personal Manuscripts]\n* {{IMDb name}}\n* {{Gutenberg author|id=1668}}\n\n{{Richard Nixon}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title=Offices and distinctions\n|list1=\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-par|us-hs}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Jerry Voorhis]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Member of the [[List of United States Representatives from California|U.S. House of Representatives]] from [[California's 12th congressional district]]|years=1947\u20131950}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Patrick J. Hillings]]}}\n\n{{s-par|us-sen}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Sheridan Downey]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of United States Senators from California|United States Senator (Class 3) from California]]|years=1950\u20131953|alongside=[[William F. Knowland|William Knowland]]}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Thomas Kuchel]]}}\n\n{{s-ppo}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Frederick F. Houser]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]] nominee for [[United States Senator|U.S. Senator]] from [[California]]<br />([[Classes of United States Senators|Class 3]])|years=[[1950 United States Senate election in California|1950]]}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Thomas Kuchel]]}}\n\n{{s-bef|before=[[Earl Warren]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]] [[List of United States Republican Party presidential tickets|nominee]] for Vice President of the United States|years=[[1952 United States presidential election|1952]], [[1956 United States presidential election|1956]]}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Henry Cabot Lodge Jr.]]}}\n\n{{s-bef|before=[[Dwight D. Eisenhower]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]] [[List of United States Republican Party presidential tickets|nominee]] for President of the United States| years=[[1960 United States presidential election|1960]]}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Barry Goldwater]]}}\n\n{{s-bef|before=[[William F. Knowland]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]] nominee for [[Governor of California]]|years=[[1962 California gubernatorial election|1962]]}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Ronald Reagan]]