os]], [[Volos Airport|Volos]], [[Zakynthos International Airport|Zakynthos]] <br /> '''Seasonal charter:''' [[Grantley Adams International Airport|Barbados]],<ref name=\"TUIcruises\"/> [[La Romana International Airport|La Romana]],<ref name=\"TUIcruises\">{{cite web|title=Arrival and departure by plane|url=https://www.tuicruises.com/an-und-abreise/flug|website=tuicruises.com|date=27 March 2020}}</ref> [[Sangster International Airport|Montego Bay]]<ref name=\"TUIcruises\"/>\n<!-- -->\n| [[Corendon Airlines]]<ref name=\"Corendon\">{{cite web|url=https://www.corendonairlines.com/en/flights/flights-to-izmir|title=Flights to Izmir|website=corendonairlines.com}}</ref> | [[Izmir Adnan Menderes Airport|Izmir]] <br> '''Seasonal:''' [[Antalya Airport|Antalya]], [[Milas\u2013Bodrum Airport|Bodrum]] (begins 2 May 2020),<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.corendonairlines.com/en/flights/flights-to-bodrum|title=Flights to Bodrum|publisher=corendonairlines.com}}</ref> [[Gazipa\u015fa Airport|Gazipa\u015fa]], [[Erkilet International Airport|Kayseri]] (begins 24 May 2020)\n<!-- -->\n| [[Corendon Airlines Europe]] | [[Hurghada International Airport|Hurghada]] <br> '''Seasonal:''' [[Heraklion International Airport|Heraklion]] (begins 2 May 2020),<ref>{{cite web |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=Corendon Airlines S20 Network expansion |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/289062/corendon-airlines-s20-network-expansion/ |website=Routesonline |accessdate=27 January 2020}}</ref> [[Rhodes International Airport|Rhodes]], [[Ben Gurion Airport|Tel Aviv]] <br>'''Seasonal charter:''' [[Banjul International Airport|Banjul]]<ref>https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/283929/corendon-airlines-europe-adds-germany-gambia-routes-in-s19/</ref> \n<!-- -->\n| [[Croatia Airlines]] | [[Split Airport|Split]], [[Zagreb Airport|Zagreb]] <br />'''Seasonal:''' [[Dubrovnik Airport|Dubrovnik]], [[Rijeka Airport|Rijeka]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Delta Air Lines]] | [[Hartsfield-Jackson Atlanta Internati